  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2021-07-06",
    "date": "2021-09-02T17:39:04Z",
    "text": "Better Opportunity and Outcomes for Socially Disadvantaged Talent Act of 2021 or the BOOST Act of 2021\n\nThis bill allows an exclusion from gross income, for income tax purposes, of 50% of any gain from the sale or exchange of a certified equity interest held for more than 3 years for corporations and partnerships in which a socially disadvantaged individual who is a U.S. citizen has an ownership interest."
  },
